{"singlePage": ["about"], "startSite": "06/01/2024", "filingNum": "", "onePageListNum": 10, "commentLabelColor": "#006b75", "yearColorList": ["#bc4c00", "#0969da", "#1f883d", "#A333D0"], "i18n": "CN", "themeMode": "manual", "dayTheme": "light", "nightTheme": "dark_colorblind", "urlMode": "pinyin", "script": "", "style": "", "head": "", "indexScript": "", "indexStyle": "", "bottomText": "You said that this was my fate, You said that I'd be okay", "showPostSource": 1, "iconList": {}, "UTC": 8, "rssSplit": "sentence", "exlink": {}, "needComment": 1, "allHead": "", "title": "Lost In Translation", "subTitle": "You Believe In What You Want To, But What You See Will Always Haunt You", "avatarUrl": "https://github.com/idontwanttobesaved/idontwanttobesaved.github.io/raw/main/assets/LIT.svg", "GMEEK_VERSION": "last", "displayTitle": "Essentially, Who am I?", "ogImage": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Meekdai/meekdai.github.io/logo64.jpg", "primerCSS": "<link href='https://mirrors.sustech.edu.cn/cdnjs/ajax/libs/Primer/21.0.7/primer.css' rel='stylesheet' />", "postListJson": {"P1": {"htmlDir": "docs/post/Pilot.md.html", "labels": ["translation"], "postTitle": "Pilot.md", "postUrl": "post/Pilot.md.html", "postSourceUrl": "https://github.com/idontwanttobesaved/idontwanttobesaved.github.io/issues/1", "commentNum": 0, "wordCount": 2566, "description": "# Odyssey 5 \n## \u4e2d\u8bd1\u540d\u300a\u592a\u7a7a\u4e94\u4eba\u7ec4\u300b\u2014\u2014\u4f60\u53ef\u80fd\u9519\u8fc7\u7684\u795e\u7ea7\u79d1\u5e7b\u5267\n\n### Intro \u5f00\u573a\u767d\n> We saw the Earth destroyed and in a heartbeat, everything and everyone we knew was gone\n\u6211\u4eec\u76ee\u7779\u5730\u7403\u6bc1\u706d\uff0c\u8f6c\u77ac\u4e4b\u95f4\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u6240\u77e5\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u4e0e\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u7686\u5df2\u6d88\u901d\uff1b\n> There were five of us: the crew of the space shuttle Odyssey, and we were the only survivors\n\u6211\u4eec\u4e94\u4eba\u2014\u2014\u592a\u7a7a\u68ad\u5965\u5fb7\u8d5b\u53f7\u7684\u5168\u4f53\u4e58\u5458\u2014\u2014\u6210\u4e3a\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u5e78\u5b58\u8005\uff1b\n> A mysterious being who called himself The Seeker rescued us and sent us back in time\n\u4e00\u4f4d\u81ea\u79f0\u201c\u5bfb\u89c5\u8005\u201d\u7684\u795e\u79d8\u5b58\u5728\u6551\u4e86\u6211\u4eec\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u6211\u4eec\u9001\u56de\u8fc7\u53bb\uff1b\n> And now we have five years to live over. Five years to discover who or what destroyed the Earth. Five years to stop it from happening... again\n\u5982\u4eca\u6211\u4eec\u62e5\u6709\u4e94\u5e74\u65f6\u5149\u91cd\u65b0\u7ecf\u5386\uff0c\u4e94\u5e74\u65f6\u95f4\u67e5\u660e\u6bc1\u706d\u5730\u7403\u7684\u5143\u51f6\uff0c\u4e94\u5e74\u673a\u4f1a\u963b\u6b62\u707e\u96be\u91cd\u6f14\n\n### Plot \u5267\u60c5\n\u4e00\u6b21\u4f8b\u884c\u822a\u5929\u4efb\u52a1\u4e2d\uff0c\u5730\u7403\u5728\u4ed6\u4eec\u773c\u524d\u5316\u4e3a\u706b\u7403\u3002", "top": 0, "createdAt": 1760426853, "style": "", "script": "", "head": "", "ogImage": "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Meekdai/meekdai.github.io/logo64.jpg", "createdDate": "2025-10-14", "dateLabelColor": "#0969da"}}, "singeListJson": {}, "labelColorDict": {"bug": "#d73a4a", "documentation": "#0075ca", "duplicate": "#cfd3d7", "enhancement": "#a2eeef", "good first issue": "#7057ff", "help wanted": "#008672", "invalid": "#e4e669", "question": "#d876e3", "translation": "#aaaaaa", "wontfix": "#ffffff"}, "faviconUrl": "https://github.com/idontwanttobesaved/idontwanttobesaved.github.io/raw/main/assets/LIT.svg", "homeUrl": "https://idontwanttobesaved.github.io", "prevUrl": "disabled", "nextUrl": "disabled"}